{"tid":2416501,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"專家：科興拖低群體免疫  BioNTech有效率更高將運港 市民宜稍等","createTime":"2021-02-21T06:12:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-21T11:02:43.000Z","uid":25558,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"9a10ef48f6b3a9c671e855853eead719a3bea8cb","tid":2416501,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T06:12:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210221/CGPENQ3LCRG65KVSYNXSWHO7JY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210221%2FCGPENQ3LCRG65KVSYNXSWHO7JY%2F&d=0FWZMlR46yIxX%2BJDTULvnftobIAPz7vP9zHpdy2ENqg%3D&h=f8f1f3c1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210221%2FCGPENQ3LCRG65KVSYNXSWHO7JY%2F&h=0e1c4123\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210221/CGPENQ3LCRG65KVSYNXSWHO7JY/</a><br />\n<br />\n專家：科興拖低群體免疫 <br />\nBioNTech有效率更高將運港 市民宜稍等<br />\n<br />\n【武肺第四波】<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：網民製開源App助記錄行程<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】日內開打的科興疫苗有效率只有50.65%，也未有足夠第三期臨床研究數據證明60歲或以上長者的保護效益。香港大學微生物學系臨床助理教授薛達指出，科興疫苗有效率較低，會拖低群體免疫，若想本港達到群體免疫，需要較多人接種德國BioNTech疫苗。另一港大教授高本恩亦認為，科興會拖低群體免疫，現時疫情受控，港人未必需要急於接種科興。<br />\n<br />\n衞生署轄下聯合科學委員會主席之一的劉宇隆周五表示，疫苗接種覆蓋率須達全民人口六、七成才有望讓香港生活回復正常。但薛達表示，以武肺病毒傳染力一般一人可傳染2.5人推算，即使疫苗有效率達100%，也需約60%人口接種疫苗，才能產生群體免疫。當疫苗有效率減少，需要更多人接種疫苗才產生群體免疫。以簡單統計學及只接種一款疫苗推算，因科興疫苗有效率只有約50%，即使全港人口都接種科興，也不足以產生群體免疫。至於同樣即將可接種的德國BioNTech疫苗，有效率較高，有66%人接種已足夠產生群體免疫。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：科委會：無證據指接種能減病毒傳播<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/RGkHi4O6GDhgbBiAtNEh6VDImmo=/1814x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/RD3QSMLENVBWVE25CI4AGOJ42Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FRGkHi4O6GDhgbBiAtNEh6VDImmo%3D%2F1814x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FRD3QSMLENVBWVE25CI4AGOJ42Q.jpg&h=583367ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■港大教授高本恩認為科興疫苗有效率較低，港人毋須急於接種。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n科興有效率僅約五成<br />\n<br />\n現時政府安排港人同........<br />\n<br />\n薛達表示，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n放寬防疫需2/3人免疫<br />\n<br />\n港大公共衞生學院教授高本恩也認為，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n他認為政府可訂購多些BioNTech或莫德納疫苗，「現時市民未必要急於接種科興疫苗，因疫情已受控，我們可以等所有BioNTech來港及接種」。"},{"pid":"2643c86ade480f6d59d6303fec5b66360a8bdcd3","tid":2416501,"uid":305358,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T06:14:41.000Z","msg":"高本恩教授會唔會好快畀港大炒？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e153ac1c0d12e4c8f63623cdc161a8b20c3b33c","tid":2416501,"uid":321803,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T06:15:00.000Z","msg":"-166% 都只係較低<br />\n<br />\n班專家食屎啦"},{"pid":"0990396aa10ed2458075985b3d668c16320a8287","tid":2416501,"uid":2959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T06:15:10.000Z","msg":"竟然有人講真話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42c5f3926c221f0b2e81c552c0d9f0d978eed6c7","tid":2416501,"uid":171313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T06:16:07.000Z","msg":"專家好勇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d84e0de7a3177f47904fadcfb702e726d327afc1","tid":2416501,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T06:16:58.000Z","msg":"英美好過中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db7901b6d05e380cf50beaf60d14f099c41198c3","tid":2416501,"uid":173060,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T06:18:19.000Z","msg":"科興咪留俾3萬隻同高官囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4692367c71c044e3a59d54e8a23ae114c6a3a04a","tid":2416501,"uid":343356,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"2643c86ade480f6d59d6303fec5b66360a8bdcd3","tid":2416501,"uid":305358,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy"